
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 06 of Thoracic MRT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Pneumothorax' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Apical pneumothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Anterolateral pneumothorax' radio button is enabled
And 'Seropneumothorax' radio button is enabled

And 'Small' radio button is enabled
And 'Large' radio button is enabled
And 'Subtotal' radio button is enabled

And 'Max. width, axial plane' input field is enabled

And 'Mediastinal shift' checkbox is enabled

And 'Atelectasis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Soft tissue emphysema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pneumopericardium' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pneumomediastinum' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Mediastinal shift' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
